            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "H-Hello... Kyah! Oh, it's just dust and cobwebs..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Umm, is anyone here...? I'm coming in."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "If there's like any human bones in here, it'll be really scary..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Urgh, now I'm starting to get scared.<CR>I shouldn't have thought of something<CR>like that..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Umm, I'm not afraid, I'm not afraid... Even if a skeleton ghost appears, we can talk everything out..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc8,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "...I feel like a talking skeleton would be even scarier..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xca,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Waaah, I should stop thinking now. I'm investigating, I'm investigating..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I guess there's nothing out of the ordinary here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "H-Hello... Kyah!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What!? What's wrong!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I got a cobweb on my face..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x126,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "D-Don't scare me. I thought maybe you found someone."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "...I guess no one's here.<CR>There's no signs of any humans."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x127,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "A deserted village... Well, I guess that's only natural, since this case is about all the villagers disappearing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "But there's a possibility that something tragic might've happened here..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Something tragic...? Like what!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I don't know, but...what would you do if we found some human bones here?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7e,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Don't start saying weird stuff like that! Could you be, like, s-scared or something?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "If I had to guess, I think I'd be scared..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x82,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Y-You're such a child. I wish you'd be more like me and keep your head up high."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x83,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Listen, even if a ghost appears, I'll smack it down!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x87,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "You'll be safe with me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I see. Then I'm relieved... Ukyah!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x125,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Wh-Wh-Wh-What!? A ghost!?<CR>Did you see a ghost!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "No, no, I got another cobweb on my face..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "D-D-Don't scare me..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I guess there's nothing out of the ordinary here."
